 ISIS thugs using sledgehammers and AK-47 rifles to destroy walls in Iraq 's UNESCO World Heritage city of Hatra .
In the seven minute footage , jihadists are shown smashing shrines and statues in the 2,000-year old city .
Militants are also recorded chipping away at the bases of ancient city pillars .
ISIS claim ancient relics are ` false idols ' which violates their fundamentalist interpretation of Islamic law .